          "rate": 0.0,
          "tax_rate": 0.0,
          "price": 0.0,
          "org_id": 38147,
          "description": "\r\nBAGHDAD \"CUTFLOWER\" AGRICULTURAL - \r\nBaghdad, Iraq\r\nProject Description\r\n\r\n\r\nCUTFLOWER is an agricultural project located in Baghdad, Iraq, with a total built-up area of approximately \r\n21,600 m2, integrating parking and loading areas, network of climate-controlled hydroponic growing zones,\r\npost-harvest facilities, water treatment, water management stations, water tanks, solar panels areas, \r\nequipment and storage areas, packaging and logistics areas, administrative offices, control room, \r\nstaff accommodations, and visitor access zones.\nThe project prioritizes water-efficient irrigation, sustainable pest control, and energy-smart technologies, \r\naiming to ensure long-term productivity and ecological balance.",
